Usage: dumpMultiBitFlopMappingFile [-help] [-mapOutputPins {false true all}]
                                   [-output <directory>]
                                   [-prefix <fileName_prefix>]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-mapOutputPins {false true all}     # Dump mapped output terms in MBFF pin
                                    # mapping file. Default is false
                                    # (enum, optional)
-output <directory>                 # Specifies the directory to dump MBFF
                                    # mapping files. Default is current
                                    # directory. (string, optional)
-prefix <fileName_prefix>           # Specifies the prefix to the MBFF mapping
                                    # files. Default is none. (string, optional)